    "content": "-------------------------------------------------------------------------------\r\n                        Lips are Movin - Meghan Trainor\r\n-------------------------------------------------------------------------------\r\nTabbed by: rlhoyt\r\n\r\nTuning: Standard\r\n\r\nThis song is pretty basic and starts on G. There are a few pauses in the song, so you'll just \r\nhave to listen for those. Also, there is a baritone sax that does something different from the bass\r\nthat I couldnt quite get.\r\n\r\nIntro:\r\n\r\n[tab]G|---------------------------------------------------------------------------|\r\nD|---------------------------------------------------------------------------|\r\nA|---------------------------3----33-----------------------------------------|\r\nE|---3----33-----5-----55---------------3------------------------------------|[/tab]\r\n\r\nThe rest of the song:\r\n\r\n[tab]G|---------------------------------------------------------------------------|\r\nD|---------------------------------------------------------------------------|\r\nA|------------------------------3----33--------------------------------------|\r\nE|--0-1-2-3----33----5----55---------------3---------------------------------|[/tab]\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n| /  slide up\r\n| \\  slide down\r\n| h  hammer-on\r\n| p  pull-off\r\n| ~  vibrato\r\n| +  harmonic\r\n| x  Mute note\r\n===============================================================================",
